title: Microsoft Intune: Certificate Connectors
agents: intune
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the status of certificate connectors configured
 in Microsoft Intune.

 The service is {OK}, if the connector has the status "active".
 If the connector has a different state, then the services is {CRIT}.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft Intune}.

item:
 The name of the intune connector.

discovery:
 One service is created for each intune connector.
